    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Books containing records of naming ceremonies within a community, usually a church group. These also serve as civic documents, recording approximate dates of birth and names of newborns, parents, and sponsors in the community.</Note_Text>
